      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/50 max-w-[720px] mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        The dataset is multi-modal and outcome-labeled. That combination is what makes it
        different from every other health corpus on the planet.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="p-8 bg-bg-surface border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl">
        <div class="text-[11px] text-accent uppercase tracking-[2px] font-semibold mb-3">Text</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Two-way coaching dialogues</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
          The texture of how Heather coaches — how she asks questions, frames numbers, and
          moves a client from "I screwed up" to "here's the next play." Pattern-level, not personal.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8 bg-bg-surface border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl">
        <div class="text-[11px] text-accent uppercase tracking-[2px] font-semibold mb-3">Images</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Food photos, menus, labels</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
          Restaurant menus before business dinners. Food logs from hotel rooms. Product
          labels from grocery aisles. Progress photos over months. Coaching happens where
          the real decisions live.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8 bg-bg-surface border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl">
        <div class="text-[11px] text-accent uppercase tracking-[2px] font-semibold mb-3">Longitudinal</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Multi-year weight trajectories</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
          The full shape of behavior change — not just outcomes, but how they tend to unfold.
          Gradual losses, regain cycles, long maintenance arcs. The methodology accounts for
          where most people actually live.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8 bg-bg-surface border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl">
        <div class="text-[11px] text-accent uppercase tracking-[2px] font-semibold mb-3">Outcome-labeled</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Patterns tied to outcomes</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
